module.exports = {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"anton072.github.io","author":"Katsushi Ougi"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"/Users/ougi/Project/anton072.github.io/src/pages/entry/2018-08-13.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","html":"<p>firebase-cliで作った環境とcreate-react-appで作った環境をマージする方法のメモ。\nまずはfirebase-project(仮)というディレクトリを作り、<code class=\"language-text\">firebase init</code>でFirebaseプロジェクトを作成します。ここでの選択は作りたいFirebaseアプリの内容を機能を選択してください。</p>\n<p>次に<code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app react-project</code>というコマンドで、react-projectディレクトリにReactプロジェクトを作ります。</p>\n<p>react-projectディレクトリからfirebase-projectディレクトリへ、</p>\n<ul>\n<li>publicディレクトリ(firebase-project配下のpublicディレクトリは削除してOK)</li>\n<li>srcディレクトリ</li>\n<li>package.json</li>\n</ul>\n<p>の3つをコピーします。以下のようになります。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534172320/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/screen.png\" alt=\"ディレクトリ構成\"></p>\n<p>コピーしたら<code class=\"language-text\">yarn install</code>でnode_modulesをインストールし、<code class=\"language-text\">yarn start</code>を実行すると下記のような画面になります。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534172784/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/react-screen.png\" alt=\"create-react-app\"></p>\n<p>これはただcreate-react-appのローカルサーバーが起動しただけで、この状態だとFirebaseにアクセスはできません。Firebaseのnode_moduleをインストールします。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ yarn add firebase</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>src/config/firebase.jsonを新規作成します。\nFirebase管理画面をブラウズして、「ウェブアプリに Firebase を追加」をクリックします。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534173232/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/screen2.png\" alt=\"Firebase管理画面\"></p>\n<p>以下のスニペットから必要な部分をコピーします。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534173232/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/screen3.png\" alt=\"Firebase管理画面\"></p>\n<p>コピーした内容をsrc/config/firebase.jsonに反映して保存します。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"apiKey\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxx\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"authDomain\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxx.firebaseapp.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"databaseURL\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://xxxxxxxx.firebaseio.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"projectId\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxx\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"storageBucket\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxx.appspot.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"messagingSenderId\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"xxxxxxxx\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>src/App.jsを以下のようにします。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Component <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> firebase <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'firebase/app'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> firebaseConfig <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./config/firebase'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> logo <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./logo.svg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">App</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">componentDidMount</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Firebase初期化</span>\n    firebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initializeApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>firebaseConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>header className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App-header\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>logo<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App-logo\"</span> alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"logo\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App-title\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Welcome to React<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>header<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App-intro\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          To <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> started<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> edit <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>code<span class=\"token operator\">></span>src<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>App<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>code<span class=\"token operator\">></span> and save to reload<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>componentDidMountでfirebaseを初期化しています。これでFirebaseにアクセスが可能になりました。</p>\n<p>試しにFirebaseの匿名ログイン機能を使ってみます。\n以下の手順で機能を有効化します。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534173232/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/screen4.png\" alt=\"Firebase管理画面\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534173232/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/screen5.png\" alt=\"Firebase管理画面\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534173232/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/screen6.png\" alt=\"Firebase管理画面\"></p>\n<p>src/App.jsを以下のように変更します。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Component <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'firebase/auth'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">App</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">componentDidMount</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Firebase初期化</span>\n    firebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initializeApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>firebaseConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 匿名ログインの実行</span>\n    firebase\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">signInAnonymously</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// ログインに失敗したときの処理</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ログインのステート変更をリッスン</span>\n    firebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">onAuthStateChanged</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> uid <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>uid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>匿名ログイン機能からUIDを取得できました。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/db5iqrybr/image/upload/v1534173232/anton072.github.io/2018-08-13/screen7.png\" alt=\"匿名ログインに成功\"></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"FirebaseとCreate React Appを共存する","date":"August 13, 2018","description":"FirebaseとCreate React Appを共存する方法","tags":["Firabase","React","JavaScript"]}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/entry/2018-08-13/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/entry/2018-08-11/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"IPアドレスから都道府県を調べる","tags":["Node","JavaScript"]}},"next":null}}


